---
import Layout from "#layouts/Layout.astro";
import backgroundImage from "#assets/images/background-2.webp";
---

<Layout title="About Us - Alefoods">
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-dvh lg:flex-row">
    <!-- Imagen - Mobile: altura automática, Desktop: background image en columna -->
    <div
      class="w-full h-[50vh] sm:h-[60vh] lg:h-auto lg:min-h-screen lg:w-1/2 lg:bg-cover lg:bg-center lg:bg-no-repeat lg:sticky lg:top-0"
      style={`background-image: url('${backgroundImage.src}')`}
    >
      <img
        src={backgroundImage.src}
        alt="Imagen de fondo."
        class="w-full h-full object-cover lg:hidden"
      />
    </div>
    <!-- Contenido - Mobile: altura automática, Desktop: puede extenderse -->
    <div
      class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center bg-green-200 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20"
    >
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-2 sm:space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h1
            class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-start mb-6 sm:mb-8"
          >
            ROOTED IN PERU, CRAFTED WITH CARE.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
            At Alefoods, we bring the authentic taste of Peru to the world. We
            specialize in exporting high-quality, natural foods, including our
            select coffee from Oxapampa and ready-to-eat quinoa from the Andes.
            Our mission is to deliver exceptional flavor and nutrition while
            upholding the highest standards of quality and social
            responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3">
            Our Vision
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
            To be recognized nationally and internationally by the most
            demanding markets as a high-quality food exporting company, creating
            well-being for all our customers, suppliers, and collaborators.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3">
            Our Mission
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
            To be exporters of food to the world, meeting our customers’ quality
            expectations, caring for the environment, and acting with corporate
            social responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="y-4 sm:y-6 md:y-8">
          <button
            class="rounded-xl bg-green-600 text-white px-6 sm:px-8 md:px-10 py-3 sm:py-4 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
          >
            <a href="/products"> Explore Our Products </a>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
